Workshop Joseph, Drawing station.

For the workshop that Joseph gave us we had to prepare an ingredient(fruit) to bring for the class, and printed pages of your whole body scaled on and 11 A3's.
-
Joseph gave us in class the assignment to hack something within 20 minuts. I teamed up with louis and hacked the color system of the brick outside in front of the entrance wijnhaven. 
the color system of the bricks in front on wijnhaven are coloured white and black in groups of 20 bricks. we coloured one of the white bricks black by placing black paper on top.
-
With all the ingredients that the class brought os homework joseph made a smoothie to collectively make and drink. 
-
with the printed body on A3's in group formations we had to make new body's by merging different body's together, hacking the body and creating something new but unnatural.
At the end of the workshop all the groups presented their hacked body's which also showed us that hacking could aslo become something unreal (autonomous).
