Final Project
-
in group formation we decided to hack the sport gym.
the idea came out of the demotivaiton of yorben who doesnt enjoyed going to the gym because of paying for it and not gaining anything form it.
from the demotivation we thought of giving the sporters in the gym somehting back, free gym.
we made a connection between the electricity company and the gym.
the description of the hack:
Your electricity company offers an in house gym where you can go to for free, by working out in their gym you gaing points which your can use to get discounts on your electricity  bill.
-
the outcome is a tell sell commercial.
-
taks were evenly divided in the group, individually everyone had their own responsibility.
my responsibility was to think out the script for the commercial and type down what the set is going to be like.
-
link to the commercial video:
https://youtu.be/1ligJZKOAgc
